      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting a rare opportunity for the most discerning buyer. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish without a single chip or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state, with the upholstery and trim showing no signs of wear and all electronic features functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is impeccable, having been meticulously maintained to ensure it drives exactly as it did the day it was manufactured. This is truly a 'time capsule' example that requires nothing but a new home.",
