    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014it's basically been pampered since day one! It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've taken such good care of it, and it really shows. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
