    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in concours-level condition, having been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. Every detail, from the pristine interior to the flawless exterior finish, reflects a standard of care synonymous with showroom quality. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle in truly peerless condition.",
