    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and staying on top of every single detail. It drives like an absolute dream and is totally ready for its next adventure. You won't find another one this clean! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
